<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="SitePreferences">  <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/Main/SitePreferences">SitePreferences</a> </h1>
<p></p>

<span class='foswikiIcon'><img src='/pub/System/DocumentGraphics/help.png' width='16' height='16' alt='help' /></span>
Foswiki's default preferences are located in <a href="/bin/view/System/DefaultPreferences">DefaultPreferences</a>, however settings defined here have override priority and should be used for local customisations.
<p></p>

<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Appearance"> Appearance </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Shortcuts"> Shortcuts </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Figures"> Figures </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Disable_Plugins"> Disable Plugins </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#LaTeX_Mode_Plugin"> LaTeX Mode Plugin </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#LaTeX_preamble"> LaTeX preamble </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#File_attachments"> File attachments </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Finalisation"> Finalisation </a>
</li></ul> 
</div>
<p></p>

<div class="">
<form method="post" action="https://damask.mpie.de/bin/viewauth/Main/SitePreferences" enctype="multipart/form-data" name="editpreferences" onsubmit="StrikeOne.submit(this)"><input type='hidden' name='validation_key' value='?8a5ff566c36c557005c736ed6eb4cb02' /><input name="prefsaction" type="hidden" value="edit" /><input type="submit" name="edit" value="Edit Preferences" class="foswikiRequiresChangePermission foswikiButton" /></form>
</div>
<p></p>

<h2 id="Appearance">  Appearance </h2>
<p class='p'>Customize logo and tooltip texts:</p>
 <ul>
<li> Set WIKILOGOIMG = 
</li> <li> Set WIKILOGOALT = Powered by Foswiki, The Free and Open Source Wiki
</li> <li> Set WIKILOGOURL = <a href="https://damask.mpie.de/bin/view/Home/WebHome">https://damask.mpie.de/bin/view/Home/WebHome</a>
</li></ul> 
<p class='p'>Give your site a specific name:</p>
 <ul>
<li> Set WIKITOOLNAME = DAMASK
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

Customize your <span class='externalLink'><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Favicon">favicon</a></span>:
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set FAVICON = /pub/System/ProjectLogos/favicon-damask.ico
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

Copyright notice: <ul>
<li> Set WEBCOPYRIGHT = <span class="foswikiRight"> <a href="http://foswiki.org/"><img src="/pub/System/ProjectLogos/foswiki-logo.svg" alt="This site is powered by Foswiki" title="This site is powered by Foswiki" width="130"/></a></span>Copyright by the contributing authors. All material on this collaboration platform is the property of the contributing authors. <br /> Ideas, requests, problems regarding DAMASK? <a href='mailto:damask@mpie.de?subject=DAMASK%20Feedback%20on%20Main.SitePreferences'>Send feedback</a><br />ยง <a href="https://www.mpie.de/imprint" target="_blank">Imprint</a> ยง <a href="https://www.mpie.de/3392182/data-protection" target="_blank">Data Protection</a>
</li></ul> 
<p class='p'>The overall skin:</p>
 <ul>
<li> Set SKIN = damask,famfamfam,pattern
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

Skin styles: <ul>
<li> Set FOSWIKI_LAYOUT_URL = /pub/System/PatternSkinThemeFatWilly/layout.css
</li> <li> Set FOSWIKI_STYLE_URL = /pub/System/PatternSkinThemeDamask/style.css
</li> <li> Set FOSWIKI_COLORS_URL = /pub/System/PatternSkinThemeFatWilly/colors.css
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

Theme variants: <ul>
<li> Set PATTERNSKIN_COLUMNS = /pub/System/PatternSkinThemeDamask/column_right.css
</li> <li> Set PATTERNSKIN_THEME_VARIANT = 
</li></ul> 
Navigation: <ul>
<li> Set PATTERNSKIN_NAVIGATION_TOPIC = System/PatternSkinThemeDamaskNavigation
</li></ul> 
Top bar: <ul>
<li> Set WEBHEADERART = <a href='/pub/System/ProjectLogos/DAMASK.png' title='https://damask.mpie.de/pub/System/ProjectLogos/DAMASK.png'  class='imageHref imageSimple imageSimple_none '  data-orig-width='2240' data-orig-height='100'><img src='/pub/System/ProjectLogos/DAMASK.png' alt='DAMASK.png' width='2240' height='100'   /></a></li> <li> Set WEBHEADERBGCOLOR = 
</li></ul> 
Coloring: <ul>
<li> Set FILECOLOR = <span class='foswikiMaroonFG'>
</li> <li> Set FIGURECOLOR = #f4fcf4
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

Additional style changes: <ul>
<li> Set USERSTYLEURL = 
</li> <li> Set DPSYNTAXHIGHLIGHTERPLUGIN_THEME = default
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

</span>
<p></p>

<h2 id="Shortcuts">  Shortcuts </h2>
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set THEROOT = <em>DAMASK</em>
</li> <li> Set THEBIN = <em>DAMASK_BIN</em>
</li> <li> Set UPTOC = <span style="float: right;"><a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="#TableOfContents"><span class='foswikiIcon'><img src='/pub/System/DocumentGraphics/parent_gray.png' width='16' height='16' alt='parent_gray' /></span></a></span>
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

<h2 id="Figures">  Figures </h2>
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set FIGURESTYLE = width:50%; float:right; background:#f4fcf4; margin: 8pt 0pt 8pt 16pt;
</li> <li> Set WIDEFIGURESTYLE = clear:both; width:100%; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background:#f4fcf4;
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

<h2 id="Disable_Plugins">  Disable Plugins </h2>
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set DISABLEDPLUGINS = 
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

<h2 id="LaTeX_Mode_Plugin"> LaTeX Mode Plugin </h2>
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set LATEXMODEPLUGIN_DENSITY = 600
</li> <li> Set LATEXMODEPLUGIN_SCALE = 0.2
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

<h2 id="LaTeX_preamble"> LaTeX preamble </h2>
<p class='p'>Customize the LaTeX preamble</p>
 <ul>
<li> Set PREAMBLE =                                        \PassOptionsToPackage{usenames,dvipsnames}{color}   \usepackage{color}   \usepackage{tikz}   \usepackage{amsmath,amssymb,amsfonts}   \usepackage[load-configurations=version-1]{siunitx}   \usepackage{subeqnarray}   \usepackage{miller}   \usepackage[format=hang]{subfig}   \usepackage{booktabs}   \usepackage{bm}   \usepackage{graphicx}   \DeclareGraphicsExtensions{.pdf,.png}
</li></ul> 
<p class='p'></p>

<p class='p'></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set LATEXPREAMBLE =                                        \PassOptionsToPackage{usenames,dvipsnames}{color}   \usepackage{color}   \usepackage[load-configurations=version-1]{siunitx}   \usepackage{miller}   \usepackage{bm}
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

<h2 id="File_attachments">  File attachments </h2>
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set ATTACHFILESIZELIMIT = 262144
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

<h2 id="Finalisation">  Finalisation </h2>
<p></p>

<code>FINALPREFERENCES</code> locks site-level preferences that are <strong>not</strong> allowed to be overridden by <a href="/bin/view/Main/WebPreferences">WebPreferences</a> or user preferences:
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set FINALPREFERENCES = ATTACHFILESIZELIMIT, PREVIEWBGIMAGE, WIKITOOLNAME, WIKIHOMEURL, ALLOWROOTCHANGE, DENYROOTCHANGE, USERSWEB, SYSTEMWEB, DOCWEB
</li></ul> 
<p></p>

<!-- Keep this as a security measure:
<p></p>
 <ul>
<li> Set ALLOWTOPICCHANGE = <a href="/bin/view/Main/AdminGroup">AdminGroup</a>
</li> <li> Set ALLOWTOPICRENAME = <a href="/bin/view/Main/AdminGroup">AdminGroup</a>
</li></ul> 
--></div>
<p class='p'></p>

